@MrLondon & @Alice.Sampo here! 🙌🏼 We need YOUR help! ❤️🙏🏼 Unusually, we are sharing with you the entire creative concept behind a new @BushmillsUK campaign called #SingularTales which will feature an award-winning spoken word artist! 🔥 We’re excited and proud to be directing and producing the hero film for this campaign, which will explore and celebrate human connection, which is rather poignant given how isolated we’ve been this past year… 🙌🏼🥰 With this in mind we want to bring Londoners together to star in our film which is being shot with #Bushmills on Tuesday 3rd in central London in an amazing studio. 💥 We’re creating a projection sequence that will fill the room, and our spoken word legend will be revealed on the day. 😱 If you’re 25 or over, we’re looking for Londoners that would like to help us with this project… be part of a cinematic moment as we create human connection together with people of different ages, races, and walks of life… singular tales, blended together… and join us in raising an award-winning glass of #Bushmills to toast the spirit of human partnership! 🥃🙌🏼❤️ If you’d like to be part of the filming, please DM @MrLondon with your email and ages. You could be a group of friend. On your own. Couples. We’re simply looking for beautiful people who love life and value connecting. If that’s YOU - DM @MrLondon now for Tuesdays filming. 

Many thanks from us xxx 

[AD]
In partnership with @buttonprcollective & @lemonlizardproductions ❤️🔥👊🏼

node.text:
@JR’s “Inside Outside” project sees the award-winning artist taking over 5 locations in London with street galleries featuring the portraits of school children, key workers and community heroes! ❤️🙏🏼 The aim is to build bridges through art, to celebrate a sport that is able to bring people together, whilst having conversations about diversity, feminism, racism, climate change and art itself. 💪🏼👏🏼 The project is global and has to date involved over 400,000 people from over 138 countries. Londoners working or living near the locations below might be invited to have their photo taken, so look out for invites to be part of history! ✌🏼
___________________________________________
LOCATIONS & DATES:
13 June - Tower Bridge
17, 25, 26 June - Lewisham Town Hall
18, 19, 20 June - Granary Square, Kings Cross
21 June - Bernie Grant Arts Centre, Tottenham 
23, 24 June + 7, 8 July - Royal Victoria Docks
___________________________________________
@JR is also exhibiting “JR: Chronicles” in @saatchi_gallery now and until 3rd October 2021. 
___________________________________________
🎥 @MrLondon with legal drone footage / filming by @sadiq & @mayorofldn - used with permission. 🙏🏼

@Alice.Sampo & @MrLondon join @Theo.Randall for @TheAuthenticItalianTable to learn about PDO & PGI designations on genuine Italian products - these little stickers on packaging are an easy way to spot the authentic Italian products in our supermarkets VS “Italian Sounding” imitations... you only live once, so make sure you’re eating well! ☺️💪🏼 And shopping this way will not only reward you in taste and quality, it will support the independent producers and farmers and their ancient traditions for generations to come! ❤️👏🏼🙏🏼 We prepared a Burrata with Asparagus, Pangrattato & Sage, followed by Trofie Pasta with Pesto, Potatoes & Green Beans - both recipes are in Theo’s new Italian Deli cookbook! 👌🏼👌🏼 Thanks to @ItalianChamUK @TrueItalianTaste for hosting and our wonderful friends @clerkenwellboyec1 @a_ontheroad @felicityspector @annabarnettcooks @londonispink @millykr @ks_ate_here for joining in the fun! 🇮🇹❤️🍽

@MrLondon @Alice.Sampo + @ClerkenwellBoyEC1 excited to finally experience Muse by @TomAikens - a converted Georgian town house, hidden away in the cobbled streets of Belgravia. 🥰 The exquisite 8-course tasting menu - available for lunch or dinner - is inspired by Tom’s passion for the finest local and seasonal produce. We arrived at 1pm and it was almost 4pm by the time we were crossing the road into Hyde Park. ☺️👌🏼 Muse is set up for 22 intimate covers... this feels special, private, and secluded. ⭐️ You have the excitement in the kitchen minus all the noise associated with bigger restaurants. Tom brings dishes to you personally, taking the time to chat and he explains the mind-bending attention to detail that goes into each and every dish. 👌🏼 We also loved having our starters, snacks and mains at the 1st floor kitchen, and then finishing at the downstairs kitchen for some incredible sweet treats. 🎉 There’s some wonderful theatre as you flow through service, and the details extend to porcelain, glassware and even the physical menu itself. If you’re looking for a treat, a touch of class, or simply an excuse to celebrate in-door dining all over again, this is a must visit for 2021. As always... booking essential. 🥰👏🏼 
🎥 @MrLondon 🙏🏼

@CharlieMellorDramatic owner of @TheLaughingHeart_London and Co-Founder of @BigNight.app - the food delivery platform that @LONDON has invested in along with London’s no.1 foodie @ClerkenwellBoyEC1. 🍽🔥 It’s a curated platform that features the BEST restaurants in London, available for local London delivery AND nationwide delivery! Which means the whole of the UK can now enjoy the very best of London, whether you’re in Manchester or Cornwall! 💪🏼💪🏼 We thought we’d have a little chat about Charlie, his journey, and why Big Night was created out of the COVID crisis, by the hospitality industry, to serve the hospitality industry with an ethical platform. And why people should give it a go ASAP! ☺️ You can find more details on @bignight.uk and order via www.BigNight.app 👌🏼☺️🥰🍽🔥

[AD] 🍹 @MrLondon with a @WorldClass cocktail for you… an inspired interpretation of @OldGrayRabbit’s winning “All Hands” recipe featuring @TheSingletonWhisky Dufftown 12YO 🥃 that helped him bag 2021 Global Bartender of the Year! 🎉  Level up your cocktails at home, and #DrinkBetterNotMore! 💪🏼💪🏼 ENJOY! ❤️
___________________________________________
All Hands
45ml Singleton of Dufftown 12yr 🥃 
15ml Dolin Dry Vermouth or similar 💦 
15ml 1:1 Home-made Simple Syrup - just equal parts water & sugar 💦 
15ml Lime Juice 💚
2 Dashes Green Chartreuse 💦 
2 Chopped Strawberries 🍓 
2 Basil Leaves 🍃 
___________________________________________
Method: Muddle Strawberries 🍓, Add ingredients, Shake and Fine Strain
Glassware: Rocks Glass
Ice: 🧊 Large Block - cubed will work if large block not available
Garnish: Lemon Zest Coin or as you fancy! 🍋 

Equipment: Shaker, Strainer, Fine Strainer, Muddler, Jigger (50/25), Dasher Bottle. 

#WorldClass2021 #MakeItWorldClass #PositiveDrinking #DrinkResponsibly

@MrLondon & @Alice.Sampo here! 🙌🏼 We need YOUR help! ❤️🙏🏼 Unusually, we are sharing with you the entire creative concept behind a new @BushmillsUK campaign called #SingularTales which will feature an award-winning spoken word artist! 🔥 We’re excited and proud to be directing and producing the hero film for this campaign, which will explore and celebrate human connection, which is rather poignant given how isolated we’ve been this past year… 🙌🏼🥰 With this in mind we want to bring Londoners together to star in our film which is being shot with #Bushmills on Tuesday 3rd in central London in an amazing studio. 💥 We’re creating a projection sequence that will fill the room, and our spoken word legend will be revealed on the day. 😱 If you’re 25 or over, we’re looking for Londoners that would like to help us with this project… be part of a cinematic moment as we create human connection together with people of different ages, races, and walks of life… singular tales, blended together… and join us in raising an award-winning glass of #Bushmills to toast the spirit of human partnership! 🥃🙌🏼❤️ If you’d like to be part of the filming, please DM @MrLondon with your email and ages. You could be a group of friend. On your own. Couples. We’re simply looking for beautiful people who love life and value connecting. If that’s YOU - DM @MrLondon now for Tuesdays filming. 

Many thanks from us xxx 

[AD]
In partnership with @buttonprcollective & @lemonlizardproductions ❤️🔥👊🏼
